This is a Ruby wrapper for Sunlight Foundation's Party Time API. It is a work in progress and not all API methods are accessible.

To install:
gem install sunlightpartytime

To use:
s = SunlightPartyTime.new("apikey")

Methods-
crp_id("name of legislator"): Get id # for legislator
parties(crp_id): Get all parties legislator is a benificiary of
parties_clean(crp_id): Get a cleaner format of party info for visualization
